{"tid":789021,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"啲00後好學唔學，學人食玩具煙😂","createTime":"2018-08-22T02:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T08:14:38.000Z","uid":20241,"like":25,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"186006bb98451fdc59e09121d997e76d0fc1a32c","tid":789021,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:52:03.000Z","msg":"頭先同班送水手足煙癮起，諗住搵隻00後跟車出去我地留係公司hea，點知搵唔撚到人<br />\n後尾我地係後樓梯見到隻00後煲緊支玩具煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n00後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我：喂有野做呀，你竟然里埋食玩具煙？<br />\n00後：電子煙黎架，仲有唔同味，好食過真煙<br />\n我同我手足聽到真係忍唔住笑撚左<br />\n笑住屌柒佢話，你會唔會有真人囡囡唔屌走去屌公仔性玩具呀，十下十下咁好人好姐食玩具煙，去送水啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黎手扯左佢支玩具煙飛落樓梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條友呆左咁眼濕濕返去做野<br />\n岩岩佢出左去送水我地就同老世報串話佢蛇王係後樓梯食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5cf58c32d4cd6d462a5eb8655b8a3b444bdb7d1","tid":789021,"uid":2572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:53:09.000Z","msg":"送水算唔算神工"},{"pid":"e34fb8897788f7cd4c168fe3c0a7e31202534bc2","tid":789021,"uid":2337,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:53:24.000Z","msg":"好型啊 Ching"},{"pid":"93abd66f5bcfae95275a9233c86842c2077c86dc","tid":789021,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c5cf58c32d4cd6d462a5eb8655b8a3b444bdb7d1","tid":789021,"uid":2572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T02:53:09.000Z","msg":"送水算唔算神工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T03:00:32.000Z","msg":"幾好做，送完今日啲單就收得工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d2ff4ab445bf776f55f2268833b0acbefe8eaf","tid":789021,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e34fb8897788f7cd4c168fe3c0a7e3120253